parameters:
Royal Court Official Emoni: Eh, wait a minute!? I'm suddenly
being betrayed, what's going on here!

Royal Court Official Emoni: It's because of your usual
behavior!
Clea: I think Nora has an idea, let's move forward.

Royal Court Official Emoni: Ugh... If I can't get out, I'll
hold a grudge for life.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Mage Relm: It seems like my weight is too much for this
place...
Priestess Sophia: I will stay here.

Priestess Sophia: I will go check on Nora-chan's condition.
Please be sure to take good care of her, okay?

Royal Court Official Emoni: Please don't make me say it
again! I am here for the investigation of the royal palace
ruins!

Royal Court Official Emoni: Who would willingly go to ruins
like this! Lately, I've been stuck with these kinds of jobs
and it's really getting on my nerves...

Clea: We will proceed to the upper floor, Sophia-san. Please
take care of things here.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
